  "remarks": "IMENSAZAN CONSULTANT ENGINEERS INSTITUTE (ICEI) was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Owned or controlled by, or acts on behalf of, KAA. Entities owned, controlled, or acting on behalf of the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps.\n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
